==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Longspun
<hw>Long"spun`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Spun out, or
extended, to great length; hence, long-winded; tedious.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>The <qex>longspun</qex> allegories fulsome grow,⟦br⟧
While the dull moral lies too plain below.</q>
<rj><qau>Addison.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Longspur</ent>⟦br⟧
